{"tid":2136561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣Tiffany&Co 有同事家屬確診左 同team同事都要繼續番工","createTime":"2020-08-02T08:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T10:32:49.000Z","uid":137455,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36590e2619c67414ad909e805c1153eeb14dc511","tid":2136561,"uid":137455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"Tiffany &amp;Co 有員工家屬確診，當日完全冇公佈，店舖進行大消毒就扮内部維修。<br />\n<br />\n同事媽媽確診，店舖經理Liam Yeung 要求所有同team嘅同事繼續番工。仲要出左事之後先有番2放2。<br />\n<br />\n跟住仲要求同事sell客去下個月既event，如果冇客去，個經理Liam Yeung就話而家就算公司拎左保就業計劃，如果員工工作欠佳，包括無數交，公司就會少炒人。<br />\n<br />\n而家疫情都冇人出街，點交數阿大佬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wd1zg4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwd1zg4v.jpg&h=ad8e7b49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEXq8bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEXq8bb.jpg&h=9b04517b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVmO5XS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVmO5XS.jpg&h=4a532fff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5d58be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5d58be.jpg&h=c188d478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a62c6754569a8590dc378d4ea0df13e00262a5b2","tid":2136561,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"由佢炒囉<br />\n都唔當你係人架啦"},{"pid":"276d76a0e399b8e9d65492f9f05783abdfadb302","tid":2136561,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:03:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af1989ea9e2480493b03f191fb34dd6a3e65f73f","tid":2136561,"uid":239994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"內部裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03eeaf6a